  "comment": "The Fusion 200 Zoom Spot features a single 200W LED and produces stunning light shows with a motorised zoom from 11°- 25°. Offering 7 colours plus open along with a rotating and static gobo wheel each containing 7 gobos plus open, the fixture is ideal for installation and mobile performers alike. Two bi-directional prisms (6 facet circular and 5 facet linear) further bolster the fixtures comprehensive features and a motorised zoom keeps the gobos razor sharp over any distance. The four button menu and LCD display, along with powerCON and DMX inputs/outputs, further enhance the fixture.",
